ị. Nhưng để tìm hiểu được thực sự Max và Lola muốn gì, Stan sẽ phải xem xét kỹ lưỡng mọi uẩn khúc trong câu truyện hành động về tình bạn, sự nghi ngờ và trộm cắp này...</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"10589","season":null,"vote_average":6.2,"vote_count":833},"modified":"2023-08-17T11:16:51.000Z","cast":["Pierce Brosnan","Salma Hayek Pinault","Woody Harrelson","Don Cheadle","Naomie Harris","Troy Garity","Russell Hornsby","Rex Linn","Michael Bowen","Mark Moses","Obba Babatundé","Jeff Garlin","Kate Walsh","Tom McGowan","Rachael Harris"],"director":["Brett Ratner"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Pierce Brosnan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Pierce Brosnan","tmdb_id":517,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dzXVwwJLPwiZeXOnf7YxorqVEEM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/517"},{"name":"Salma Hayek Pinault","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Salma Hayek Pinault","tmdb_id":3136,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1qfYF7NGRObmeKR7IVXUFVIC0CN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3136"},{"name":"Woody Harrelson","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Woody Harrelson","tmdb_id":57755,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/igxYDQBbTEdAqaJxaW6ffqswmUU.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/57755"},{"name":"Don Cheadle","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Don Cheadle","tmdb_id":1896,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/umhTmcVF26qZKEpSfG1ZNpcbs9D.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1896"},{"name":"Naomie Harris","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Naomie Harris","tmdb_id":2038,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/41TVAcYqKKF7PGf3x7QfaLvkLSW.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2038"},{"name":"Troy Garity","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Troy Garity","tmdb_id":31711,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eNK78vBECYQbug1h7jFVo8OeHr0.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/31711"},{"name":"Russell Hornsby","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Russell Hornsby","tmdb_id":62649,"profile":"https://image